{
  "stem": "26142.17",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "If we had enough snow, it was fine.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You could walk in the snow.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But when it froze-- it froze, you-- you slipped on that and then fall.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It was terrible.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Anyway, we worked on-- we worked on there [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] 50 days.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And in 50 days, I-- I dared myself-- I-- the-- one of the-- one of the supervisors was a Yugoslav.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And he spoke in Slavic.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And-- and he-- he, one time, gave me a piece of bread and he gave me a half a piece of a cigarette.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I thought to myself, oh, he's a nice-- nice guy.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I stupidly allowed myself and I told him-- I told him-- and this must have been, already, January-- January, February-- so I told him you better-- you better treat us nice because the war is going to-- to an end, and-- and Germany is losing the war.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And he said, you are so dumb.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "You will never get out of here alive.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I said, yeah.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's not going to last more than about 20, 30 days.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He says, you won't last 20, 30 days.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "After-- after I had this conversation with this guy, I really got-- got scared that I-- I got-- my-- my tongue was loose.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "How did I dare to talk like that?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyway, fortunately, he didn't pursue that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He didn't pursue it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and I got-- after 40 or 50 days-- I won't go into this story here, how I got beaten up.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I have no strength to-- to-- to repeat it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was the one that encouraged many others from our group not to register sick because once you get into the revier, they never see you again.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They send you to Flossenburg.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
